{
  "texts": [
    "The second part was designed to gather background and professional information from study participants.",
    "This part consisted of five single-choice questions and was used to profile the current experts in DeSci.",
    "The third part directly addressed the research questions through four open-ended exploratory questions.",
    "The complete survey is provided in the Supplementary Material (SM3).",
    "The survey was pretested by three experts in the field of DeSci to validate its comprehensibility and clarity."
  ]
}